This paper discusses the deployment patterns and demand served by LTE networks, which are related to network infrastructure (cs.NI) and security (cs.CR). The paper also mentions the impact of video traffic, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and social implications (cs.SI). Finally, the paper touches upon commercial policies, which are related to information theory (cs.IT).
